00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:21.799
you should build more shiny apps and then throw them away.

00:00:21.799 --> 00:00:27.160
So my name is James Wade. I'm a chemist and data scientist that works in a research and

00:00:27.160 --> 00:00:35.000
development environment, and I build shiny apps, a lot of them. I have lived the production

