00:18:52.959 --> 00:18:58.160
absorb it and listen. And similarly with these disposable apps, I think that's a good fit

00:18:58.160 --> 00:19:02.760
for where if they get the message, they no longer need the app, hopefully.

00:19:02.760 --> 00:19:04.359
Perfect. Thank you, James.

